Against Patrick Mahomes, no lead is safe.

Patrick Mahomes is Quarterback Absolute Value. Like @BenjaminSolak says, he is incredible at turning negative plays into positives.

Mahomes had the 2nd lowest sack rate in the NFL despite being among the most pressured QBs (also someone get Justin Fields an OLine).
